---
import sunriseTheme from '../assets/sunriseTheme.svg';
---

<div id="container">
  <img id="background" src={sunriseTheme.src} alt="Sunrise Theme Background" fetchpriority="high" />
  <main>
    <section id="why-volunteer">
      <h1>Why Volunteer with Alphabeta?</h1>
      <p>
        Volunteering with Alphabeta is more than just giving your time. It's an opportunity to learn, grow, and contribute to impactful projects that shape communities.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Showcase Your Skills:</strong> Highlight your talents in a dynamic and supportive environment.</li>
        <li><strong>Learn and Grow:</strong> Gain hands-on experience in programming, social media, and business skills.</li>
        <li><strong>Join a Team:</strong> Collaborate with experienced professionals and like-minded individuals.</li>
        <li><strong>Contribute to Projects:</strong> Make a real impact through community development initiatives.</li>
        <li><strong>Build a Portfolio:</strong> Create a track record of meaningful contributions for future opportunities.</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://forms.gle/yPgYNpYufXCZpyHC9" class="button">Get Started</a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>2024 Alphabeta - Empowering Volunteers, Building Communities</p>
  </footer>
</div>

<style>
  #background {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -1;
    filter: blur(50px);
  }

  #container {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #FFF3E0, #FFE0B2);
    color: #E65100;
  }

  main {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  #why-volunteer {
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.1);
    border: 2px solid #FF5722;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  #why-volunteer h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  #why-volunteer p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  #why-volunteer ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  #why-volunteer ul li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  #why-volunteer ul li:before {
    color: #FF5722;
    font-weight: bold;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    color: white;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #FF9800, #FF5722);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }

  .button:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #E65100, #FF5722);
  }

  footer {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #F57C00;
  }
</style>
